features: 【20-grid Large-capacity Minimalist shoe cubby】The cubby shoe rack measures 32.8*13.6*28.2 in, with 5 shoe organizer that can hold up to 20 pairs of shoes. Each shoe grid measures 7.4*11.4*4.4 in and can accommodate shoes up to size 10.5, including sports shoes, casual shoes, and high heels. Our shoe rack for closet has enough space to store various shoes that were previously piled up in corners in an orderly manner, making it easy to access and keeping the home environment clean and beautiful.

【A Better Way to Maintain Your Shoes】 Compared to traditional shoe rack organizer, our semi-open shoe organizer cabinet can be used for long-term storage during seasonal changes and short-term storage during daily shoe changes to protect your shoes from piling up, improper placement, dust, sunlight, and other damage. In addition, shoe cubby storage allow for adequate air circulation, thus enhancing breathability and preventing dampness and odors, and extending the use of your shoes.

【Maximize Space Savings】 Shoes are placed in layers, utilizing wall space and all available gaps, to minimize the amount of floor space taken up by footwear. The shoe storage closet features a stackable design, allowing two or more sets to be vertically stacked, forming a complete shoe cubby that maximizes storage space within the same floor area. This design is ideal for small spaces and high-capacity storage, enabling small spaces such as wardrobes, foyers, and corners to be fully utilized.

【Lightweight and Easy to Move】Compared to wooden shoe storage organizer, our cubby shoe rack is lightweight and easy to move, dismantle, and install when moving. The closet shoe rack comes with handles for easy transport. It can be placed in the entryway for storing shoes and holding personal items; in the wardrobe for better-organizing clothes, shoes, and accessories; in the living room as a display shelf and home decoration; or in the dressing room to provide better storage space for guests.

【Sturdy Structure and Easy to Clean】shoe closet features a sturdy frame made of anti-rust metal pipes and connectors, which provides excellent stability and load-bearing capacity. It also has a shoe holder fixing strap which further stabilizes the shoe organizer cubby so that it can bear the weight of the shoe without deforming or tilting. The shoe cube organizer is upholstered in a dustproof Oxford fabric that is soft, durable, easy to clean, and environmentally friendly.

【Not just a Shoe Rack, but also a Storage Shelf】In addition to shoes, it can hold small jewelry boxes, figurines, children's toys, decorative items, books, and clothes. The top can be used as a shelf to store commonly used items when going out, such as handbags, hats, umbrellas, keys, and wallets. When returning home, you can place your carry-on items to avoid searching for them everywhere next time you go out.

【Easy Assembly, Time-saving】 Our shoe cube package comes with a shoe storage frame, assembly tools, numbered parts, and detailed installation instructions. No professional expertise or tools are required - simply use the provided basic tools to assemble the numbered components as per the instructions and it's ready to use.

manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: Are you tired of tripping over your shoes and struggling to find the right pair? A shoe rack organizer may be the solution you need! Closet shoe organizer offer a practical and stylish way to keep your shoes organized and easily accessible. Our stackable shoe organizer are the choice for every home. Don't let cluttered shoes stress you out anymore, invest in our closet shoe rack today and experience the benefits for yourself!

Multifunctional shoe rack The top shelf serves as a display for decorative items, umbrellas, hats, keys, and other small items. The shoe compartments are designed to accommodate shoes, shoe boxes, small storage containers, clothing, accessories, toys, figurines, books, and various other items.

Shoe Maintenance The semi-open design of the cubby shoe rack is suitable for both long-term and short-term storage of shoes. It helps prevent the negative effects of stacking, improper placement, dust, sunlight, and other factors that may cause odor, reduce breathability, and shorten the lifespan of shoes. Proper shoe maintenance can effectively improve the ventilation and freshness of shoes and extend their usage duration. Sturdy and Stable Structure The shoe rack is constructed with thick, high-quality steel pipes, providing excellent durability and stability. The top shelf can bear a weight of up to 15 pounds/6.8kg, while each grid on the main frame can bear a weight of 2.2 pounds/1kg, equivalent to the weight of two 500ml/500g bottles of cola. Equipped with shoe organizer cubby fixing straps, the shoe organizer can withstand the weight of shoes without collapsing or breaking. Durable and Easy-to-Clean Fabric The shoe storage is constructed with dust-resistant Oxford fabric, which is soft, easy to clean, and highly durable. The shoe cabinet is scratch-resistant and effectively protects shoes from damage, helping to maintain their appearance and quality over time.

Suitable for Entryway Use This shoe shelf is designed to accommodate different types of shoes and other items commonly used when going out, such as handbags, hats, umbrellas, keys, and more. When returning home, it provides a convenient place to store items such as clothing, jackets, and hats, allowing for easy access and organization at the entryway. Suitable for Closet Use Effectively expands storage space in the closet, allowing you to better organize clothing, shoes, and accessories, while keeping the house tidy. Suitable for Living Room/School Dormitory/Hotel/Changing Room Use In the living room: This shoe rack organizer can double as a storage shelf, allowing for the placement of plants, decorations, small storage boxes, toys, snacks, and other items. Additionally, the stylish and minimalist design of the shoe storage organizer can serve as a home decoration, adding aesthetic appeal to the living space. In school dormitories: This closet shoe rack saves space and allows for easy storage of shoes, backpacks, stationery, and other items. In hotels: The Oxford cloth shoe cubby can be used to provide better storage space for guests, enhancing their overall stay experience. In changing rooms: This cubby shoe rack can be placed in fitness centers, swimming pools, and other changing rooms, making it easy for individuals to store their shoes and increasing space utilization.
Easy to install Thanks to clear instructions and numbered parts, you'll be putting this shoe rack together without even realizing it.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on May 17, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Say goodbye to shoe chaos and hello to an organized paradise!
reviews.reviewText: If you're tired of tripping over scattered shoes and spending precious minutes searching for a matching pair, then look no further than this shoe organizer. I've tried my fair share of storage solutions, but this innovative organizer has truly revolutionized my shoe collection.From the moment I unboxed this marvel of organization, I was impressed by its sturdy construction and design. The high-quality materials ensure durability, while the black color complements any room decor.The true beauty of this shoe organizer lies in its practicality. With its multiple tiers and adjustable compartments, I was able to effortlessly store and display my entire shoe collection. Whether it's pumps, sneakers, or boots, each pair finds its designated spot, making it easy to find and retrieve the perfect footwear for any occasion.Assembly was a breeze, thanks to the clear instructions and the thoughtful inclusion of all necessary tools. The shoe organizer feels sturdy and stable, even when fully loaded with my extensive shoe collection.This shoe organizer has surpassed my expectations in every way. It has transformed my chaotic shoe storage into a streamlined and visually pleasing display. If you're seeking a solution to tame the shoe clutter and enhance your organization, this shoe organizer is an investment you won't regret. Say goodbye to shoe chaos and hello to an organized paradise!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 30, 2024
reviews.reviewText: Checks all the boxes for me....... classic black design, slim profile, true to size, plenty of slots, made of lightweight materials that didn't break apart in transit, and most importantly really easy to put together. Would invest in another one for sure.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on May 16, 2023
reviews.reviewText: I received this product as a promotional sample for review, and I definitely like this shoe organizer. It is well built and quite sturdy when assembled. BTW, assembly is very simple and took about 15 minutes at most - thread few rods, screw few bolts, done. No extra tools required (a hex wrench is included).The material is strong and dense, and appears pretty tear-resistant. The organizer itself is quite large and spacious. Definitely has more capacity compared to my current shoe shelf. If necessary, two of them can be stacked together either side by side, or even on top of each other (the necessary fastening bolts are included).Overall, would definitely recommend.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 3, 2023
reviews.reviewText: This rack is perfect for in the closet shoe storage - it’s not the prettiest when it’s full of shoes but I love how efficiently it stores them. The cubbies are perfect for a pair of shoes, even men’s shoes. And I can fit 2-3 pairs of flip flops in 1 cubby as well. It stands fairly sturdy (enough to do the job), and for the price you can’t do better.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on September 23, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Holds so many shoes
reviews.reviewText: This shoe cubby was very easy to put together. It turned out to be really sturdy also. What I liked most about it is that it fits exactly where I needed it to - it’s not a huge area but it holds 20+ shoes. For boots I had to use 2 areas one for each boot. This really freed up so much space on our garage shelves. Love it and highly recommend it. It’s also very nice looking so it can be used inside the house as well.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on July 9, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Classy & Easy-to-Assemble Organizer
reviews.reviewText: I was looking for an organizer to go inside of my coat closet to house all of our shoes. After measuring, this seemed to fit perfectly. It arrived in a small box which made me nervous but every piece was there (some extra hardware was included). You even get the small wrenches you need so you won't need anything at all from your own toolbox. There also is hardware included to use if stacking two sets together. My 8 year old son took the lead in putting this together and we were able to have it together and in the closet in about 20 minutes. I absolutely love it! If you have a lot of boots or taller shoes, this won't be the greatest organizer (although still doable for most, it'll be a tight squeeze). There is a somewhat functional top where you could place a few things but it isn't strong enough for a storage basket or anything like that. Right now I put my kids' hats on it. I would definitely buy this again!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 23, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Easy to put together and looks nice
reviews.reviewText: I put two of these together to organize my mom's shoe situation. It made her closet way more organized. They were easy to put together and stack.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on September 20, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Sturdy and durable
reviews.reviewText: I love this shoe cubby! It holds 20 pairs of adult shoes and keeps them all organized. This is so much nicer than the tote I was using, or having them all over the floor of a closet. I can find my shoes quickly in the morning as I'm leaving for work. It is quite sturdy and holds together very well. The top is the same light weight material and we just added a blanket as that's the preferred sleeping spot for our cat. I totally recommend this for better organization.
